title: Iris- Stufstock 2004.h264.recode.avi
description:
IRIS is a well known Romanian hard rock band. It was established in 1977 by Ioan Dumitrescu (drums), Ion Olteanu (lead solo guitar and vocals) and Emil Lechin?eanu (bass guitar). They achieved huge success, followed by tours throughout Romania and recordings for radio broadcast and are one of the best Romanian rock bands. In 2006, IRIS were nominated at the MTV Romania Music Awards for Best Band, Best Rock and Best Live Act. They won Best Rock.
